                <h1>World-renowned pianist to perform for a sold-out Baldwin</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/65ae5183-57e7-4190-b236-dd0672c85e7c.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="" class="w-100">
